heuristic/pruned_bfs_search/ is a C translation of the Python `snake_in_box`
package by Daniel Ari Friedman (https://github.com/docxology/snake), whose
README states it is released under the MIT License. The translation preserves
the original logic, structure, and function names; the terms above apply to
this repository's own code, and the original project's MIT license and
copyright are acknowledged for the portions it was translated from.
